dct_title_s: Map showing property of the Wildwood Crest Company in the Borough of Wildwood Crest, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map showing property of the Wildwood Crest Company in the Borough of Wildwood Crest, New Jersey. Includes riparian grant showing bulkhead and real estate. Map area covers North Grassy Sound Channel, South Swain's Channel, West State Inland Waterway, and East Atlantic Ocean.
